title: Trait Hoarder
description: Trait Hoarder Manhwa Kim Joonsoo, a free-to-play ranker in the mobile game, “Arcane Seoul,” possessed the tutorial character, Warrior Kim! He has to survive in a merciless world as a basic character. All he has to trust is his game knowledge as a ranker and Warrior Kim’s ability to swap out traits indefinitely! 특성 쌓는 김전사
